hendrixer.github.io/nextjs-course/

- Framework. Uses react as its view library. It is opinionated.

Features that you get our of box:
- Dev build system
- Prod build system
- Prerendering: SSR, build time, static
- Routing
- API routes

Using SPA only -> Create react app
Using SPA + blog -> Use next js
Using SSR and API -> Use Next js


Installation:
------------
yarn create next-app
npx create-next-app

yarn add next react react-dom

"scripts":{
"dev":"next",
"build":"next build",
"start":"next start"
}